# Operations & Employee Hub — Data Dictionary

## Employees sheet

| Field Name           | Type        | Allowed Values / Format                           | Description |
|----------------------|------------|---------------------------------------------------|-------------|
| Employee_ID          | Text       | Unique ID (e.g., E-0001)                          | Unique identifier for each employee. |
| First_Name           | Text       | Free text                                         | Employee first name. |
| Last_Name            | Text       | Free text                                         | Employee last name. |
| Role                 | Text       | Free text                                         | Job title or role. |
| Employment_Status    | Dropdown   | Active, Onboarding, Leave, Terminated             | Current employment status. |
| Hire_Date            | Date       | YYYY-MM-DD                                        | Date of hire. |
| Days_Since_Hire      | Calculated | Integer                                           | Days since hire date. |
| Remote_Readiness     | Dropdown   | Ready, Needs Equipment, Needs Training, Not Eligible | Remote work readiness. |
| Clearance_Status     | Dropdown   | Pending, Interim, Final, Denied                   | Clearance status. |

## Equipment sheet

| Field Name           | Type        | Allowed Values / Format                           | Description |
|----------------------|------------|---------------------------------------------------|-------------|
| Employee_ID          | Text       | Must match Employees sheet                        | Links to employee. |
| Equipment_Type       | Dropdown   | Laptop, Monitor, Phone, Token, Other              | Equipment category. |
| Equipment_Status     | Dropdown   | Not Assigned, Assigned, In Transit, Returned, Lost | Current status. |
| Equipment_Due_Date   | Date       | YYYY-MM-DD                                        | Date equipment should be delivered/returned. |
